  "prompt": "How can I become member of Mensa India?",
  "response": "To become a member of Mensa India, you need to follow these steps:\n\n1. **Understand Mensa Membership Requirements**:  \n   Mensa is an organization for people who score in the top 2% of the general population on an approved intelligence test. To join, you must demonstrate this level of intelligence through an accepted test.\n\n2. **Take an Approved IQ Test**:  \n   You can take one of the following tests to qualify for Mensa India:  \n   - **Mensa India Supervised IQ Test**: Mensa India periodically conducts supervised IQ tests in various cities. You can check their official website for test schedules.  \n   - **Already Taken a Test?** If you have previously taken an approved IQ test (e.g., Stanford-Binet, WAIS, or Raven\u2019s Progressive Matrices), you can submit your scores for validation.  \n   - **International Mensa Tests**: If you are outside India, you can take a supervised test administered by another Mensa chapter and submit the results.\n\n3. **Prepare for the Test**:  \n   Mensa India provides sample questions and practice tests on their website to help you prepare. Familiarize yourself with the format and types of questions asked.\n\n4. **Register for the Test or Submit Your Scores**:  \n   - If you\u2019re taking the supervised IQ test, register through the Mensa India website and pay the required fee.  \n   - If you already have qualifying scores, submit them along with supporting documents for review.\n\n5. **Await Results**:  \n   After taking the test or submitting your scores, you\u2019ll receive your results. If your score is in the top 2%, you\u2019ll be eligible for membership.\n\n6. **Complete the Membership Process**:  \n   Once you qualify, you\u2019ll need to fill out a membership application and pay the annual membership fee to officially join Mensa India.\n\n7. **Enjoy the Benefits**:  \n   As a member of Mensa India, you\u2019ll gain access to a network of intellectually curious individuals, events, publications, and other resources.\n\n### Important Links and Resources:  \n- **Mensa India Official Website**: [https://www.mensaindia.org](https://www.mensaindia.org)  \n- **Contact Mensa India**: Check their website for contact details to inquire about test dates, fees, or other questions.\n\nGood luck with your journey to becoming a Mensa member!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
